---
title: Seared Sirloin and Demi-Glace Sauce with Caramelized Onion Mashed Potatoes and a Green Salad
description: You probably haven’t tasted steak like this before: this sirloin is spooned with a rich, luscious pan sauce to bring its meatiness to the maximum. On the side, caramelized onion and shallot mashed potatoes--along with a bright cranberry and spring mix salad--so good, you may not want to share.
